data.description: Step into this 2-story Harvard Plan with 5 bedrooms & 3 full bathrooms. The open floor plan with vaulted-ceiling great room, dining room and gourmet kitchen make it the perfect space to host memorable gatherings. This home was built in 2019 with fantastic upgrades including energy efficient kitchen appliances, granite countertops, custom wood cabinets & an attached 2-car garage. The primary suite is a spacious sanctuary with a large bath and walk-in closet, offering all the space you need to organize and indulge in relaxation.    Enjoy the easy maintenance of the xeriscaped front yard and find the perfect canvas to create your own outdoor oasis in the fully fenced back yard.    This home has been well maintained and is move-in ready!
